						<div class="postbody">A supid question probably, but do you feed the cameras with a 90x100Â° FOV or do you use the current FOV and warp the result ? Also, it seems the two frames are from a different point in time, are you doing a dual render at a given time or is the second image rendered on a subsequent frame ?</div>

