				<a name="p75131"></a>
				<div class="postauthor" style="color: #FF6633">Fredz</div>
				<div class="posterrank">Petrif-Eyed</div><div class="postavatar"><img src="./download/file.php?avatar=14042_1355057831.png" width="160" height="128" alt="User avatar" /></div>

